{"tid":318019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交通警揸綿羊仔　原來真相是......","createTime":"2017-07-11T23:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T04:50:54.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87da0006a2c3a2c1697a559ff3b40c7f66d3768d","tid":318019,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T23:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499241454_de89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499241454_de89.jpg&h=fed77a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在街上見到交通警揸電單車，不足為奇，但若果交通警員襯著一部綿羊仔，又是甚麼玩法？<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499239718_08f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499239718_08f3.jpg&h=90e0e0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民見到交通警揸著綿羊仔，在旺角道出現，引起網民無限聯想。<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499239837_a813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499239837_a813.jpg&h=ad751cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有目擊市民指，該警員開動綿羊仔時，還會「響喉」，讚他有品味。<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499236609_1147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499236609_1147.jpg&h=021df7c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星爺在電影《逃學威龍2》的其中一個造型。(網上圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499236623_78be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499236623_78be.jpg&h=dbc77885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民聲稱在現場見到綿羊仔司機發生交通意外，需要送院，指警員當時應該是幫忙揸走部綿羊。(網上圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499236635_2267.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499236635_2267.jpg&h=b8e59e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意外一刻，肇事綿羊仔與巴士相撞。(網上圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170705/large/1499237559_29f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499237559_29f0.jpg&h=e5ff2459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民為警員平反。(網上截圖)<br />\n<br />\n日前有市民見到一名交通警察，揸著一架綿羊仔在旺角道一帶橫行，有網民將「奇景」放上網，還讚阿sir有品味，開車期間還「響喉」，覺得好盞鬼。<br />\n<br />\n照片隨即引起熱烈討論，有網民指即時聯想起星爺(周星馳)在電影《逃學威龍2》中扮演交通警，揸著「 薯兜」電單車的場景；還令人聯想起國家主席習大大訪港期間，接見一名男警員時發出的疑問：「這是正式錄用的警察嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n不過有自稱在現場目擊的網民則指，見到落橋位有三車相撞意外，其中電單車司機與疑與巴士相撞，受傷上了白車，「警察幫手揸返走架車」。<br />\n<br />\n為了解開這個迷思，《壹》仔問過警察公共關係科，發言人指有關詳情了解中未有回覆。但發言人指若發生交通意外，警員是有機會幫手揸走架車。<br />\n<br />\n反正阿sir就不是蛇王或者做私務，都算真相大白啦！<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：facebook 小心駕駛(討論別人駕駛態度)群組<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170705/526550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170705%2F526550&d=9Se5zqs71mdQyGISgqkvPlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=87133568\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20170705%2F526550&h=797b5fc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20170705/526550</a>"},{"pid":"bd70b3033d525ecb9220a4c1ccf2aeaf297f6e94","tid":318019,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"好盞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲似返個警察，為市民服務就係呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1181c5ece924a01b03ba1f84ddfa9ad7c70226a","tid":318019,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好盞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲似返個警察，為市民服務就係呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n陣間有人話你5毛啦"},{"pid":"c